352
00:23:02,400 --> 00:23:03,440
Nie.

353
00:23:05,170 --> 00:23:06,710
Ste si blízki?

354
00:23:09,410 --> 00:23:11,550
Ste si takí blízki,

355
00:23:13,780 --> 00:23:14,980
