00:24:02,700 --> 00:24:04,670
Boli sme predsa spolu 6 rokov.

365
00:24:06,200 --> 00:24:07,700
Skutočne mi neveríš?

366
00:24:09,470 --> 00:24:10,670
Popravde,

367
00:24:12,210 --> 00:24:13,310
